#!/usr/bin/env perl
use v5.40;

use List::Util qw(max);
use Mojo::File;
use Mojo::JSON qw(decode_json encode_json);

__PACKAGE__->run unless caller;

=encoding utf8

=head1 NAME

github-linguist-summary - make a table of the github-linguist summaries for all my repos

=head1 SYNOPSIS

	% env GITHUB_USER=... GITHUB_TOKEN=... github-linguist-summary

=head1 DESCRIPTION

I wanted to see a matrix of the [github-linguist](https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist)
results for all of my repos, so I threw this together.

=head1 SOURCE AVAILABILITY

